eSourceHighlight version 0.01
=============================

A simple text editor for not to heavy files developed with Perl/pEFL.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Syntax::SourceHighlight
  pEFL
  File::HomeDir

